title: You serious?.....
body:
Jhin's Help tooltip.

'Watch' out for traps? you JUST said they were invisible...
Thats an Oxymoron, how are you supposed to 'watch out' for something thats invisible?  The same way you 'watch out' for Teemo shrooms? by blundering blindly into them?

thats like saying 'keep an eye out' for Shaco's Q
or 'look' over your shoulder for Evelynn...

on another note, thanks for releasing Jhin :)

replies.body: better by an oracles... oh wait....
I can just imagine a Teemo Support, Jhin ADC, Caitlyn Mid, Shaco Jungle and Maokai Top
